<br />
<li> [ ] [SOLO] Buy 6 Spiderling Silk in the bazaar. Create 3 Silk Threads by combining (2) spiderling silk, and combine the 3 Silk Threads to create Silk Cord
<br />
<li> [ ] [SOLO] Buy a backpack pattern
<br />
<li> [ ] [SOLO] Combine the Silk Cord, Backpack Pattern, and Silken Tapestry to create <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=33238" target="_blank" class="postlink">Silken Tapestry Satchel</a>
