<li> [ ] [SOLO] Return to Talwyn Flamecaller in Lava Storm Mountains (-2170, -1050)
<br />
 <ul>
<br />
 <li> Hand Talwyn the Silken Tapestry Satchel (empty), and he will hand it back to you
<br />
 <li> Combine the four Prismatic Crystals, Cohesion Gem, Staff of Fluxing Power, Wisp of Pure Flame, and Shard of Pure Ice in the Silken Tapestry Satchel and you will create <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=33239" target="_blank" class="postlink">Full Tapestry Satchel</a>
<br />
 <li> Hand Talwyn the Full Tapestry Satchel. and receive the <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=33244" target="_blank" class="postlink">Staff of Prismatic Power</a>
<br />
 </ul>
<br />
</ol>
